#. Type: text
#. Description
#. Main menu item
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:4
msgid "Configure MD devices"
msgstr "Cyflunio dyfeisiau amlddisg (MD)"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:8
msgid "Multidisk (MD) not available"
msgstr "Nid yw amlddisg (MD) ar gael"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:8
msgid ""
"The current kernel doesn't seem to support multidisk devices. This should be "
"solved by loading the needed modules."
msgstr ""
"Nid yw'r cnewyllyn cyfredol yn cynnal dyfeisiau amlddisg. Dylid datrys hyn "
"gan lwytho'r modylau angenrheidiol."

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:14
msgid "Create MD device"
msgstr "Creu dyfais amlddisg (MD)"

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:14
msgid "Delete MD device"
msgstr "Dileu dyfais amlddisg (MD)"

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:14
msgid "Finish"
msgstr "Gorffen"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:15
msgid "Multidisk configuration actions"
msgstr "Gweithredion cyflunio Amlddisg"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:15
msgid "This is the Multidisk (MD) and software RAID configuration menu."
msgstr "Dyma ddewislen cyfluniad Amlddisg (MD) a RAID meddalwedd."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:15
msgid ""
"Please select one of the proposed actions to configure multidisk devices."
msgstr ""
"Dewiswch un o'r gweithredoedd awgrymwyd er mwyn cyflunio dyfeisiau amlddisg. "

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:22
msgid "No RAID partitions available"
msgstr "Dim rhaniadau RAID ar gael"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:22
msgid ""
"No unused partitions of the type \"Linux RAID Autodetect\" are available. "
"Please create such a partition, or delete an already used multidisk device "
"to free its partitions."
msgstr ""
"Doedd dim rhaniadau o'r math \"RAID Linux Awtoddarganfod\" ar gael. Crëwch y "
"fath rhaniad os gwelwch yn dda, neu dilewch dyfais amlddisg a ddefnyddir "
"eisioes er mwyn rhyddhau ei rhaniadau."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:22
msgid ""
"If you have such partitions, they might contain actual file systems, and are "
"therefore not available for use by this configuration utility."
msgstr ""
"Os oes y fath rhaniadau gennych, fe allent gynnwys systemau ffeiliau, a "
"felly nid ydynt ar gael i'w defnyddio gan yr erfyn cyfluniad hwn."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:32
msgid "Not enough RAID partitions available"
msgstr "Dim digon o rhaniadau RAID ar gael"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:32
msgid ""
"There are not enough RAID partitions available for your selected "
"configuration.  You have ${NUM_PART} RAID partitions available but your "
"configuration requires ${REQUIRED} partitions."
msgstr ""
"Does dim digon o rhaniadau RAID ar gael ar gyfer eich cyfluniad dewisiesig. "
"Mae gennych ${NUM_PART} rhaniad RAID ar gael ond mae eich cyfluniad yn mynnu "
"${REQUIRED} rhaniad."

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:39
msgid "RAID0"
msgstr "RAID0"

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:39
msgid "RAID1"
msgstr "RAID1"

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:39
msgid "RAID5"
msgstr "RAID5"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:40
msgid "Multidisk device type:"
msgstr "Math dyfais amlddisg:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:40
msgid "Please choose the type of the multidisk device to be created."
msgstr "Os gwelwch yn dda, dewiswch y math o ddyfais amlddisg i'w greu."

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:45
msgid "Number of active devices for the RAID1 array:"
msgstr "Nifer y dyfeisiau gweithredol ar gyfer yr araë RAID1:"

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:45
msgid ""
"The RAID1 array will consist of both active and spare partitions. The active "
"partitions are those used, while the spare devices will only be used if one "
"or more of the active devices fail."
msgstr ""
"Fe fydd yr araë RAID1 wedi ei gyfansoddi o rhaniadau gweithredol a sbâr. "
"Defnyddir y rhaniadau gweithredol, tra caiff y dyfeisiau sbâr eu defnyddio "
"dim ond os mae un neu fwy o'r dyfeisiau gweithredol yn methu."

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:54
msgid "Number of spare devices for the RAID1 array:"
msgstr "Nifer o ddyfeisiau sbâr ar gyfer yr araë RAID1:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:59
msgid "Spare devices for the RAID1 multidisk device:"
msgstr "Dyfeisiau sbâr ar gyfer y dyfais amlddisg RAID1:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:59
msgid "You have chosen to create an RAID1 array with ${COUNT} spare devices."
msgstr "Rydych wedi dewis creu araë RAID1 gyda ${COUNT} dyfais sbâr."

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:69
msgid "Number of active devices for the RAID5 array:"
msgstr "Nifer y dyfeisiau gweithredol ar gyfer yr araë RAID5:"

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:69
msgid ""
"The RAID5 array will consist of both active and spare partitions. The active "
"partitions are those used, while the spare devices will only be used if one "
"or more of the active devices fail. A minimum of three active devices is "
"required."
msgstr ""
"Fe fydd yr araë RAID5 wedi ei gyfansoddi o rhaniadau gweithredol a sbâr. "
"Defnyddir y rhaniadau gweithredol, tra caiff y dyfeisiau sbâr eu defnyddio "
"dim ond os mae un neu fwy o'r dyfeisiau gweithredol yn methu."

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:69
msgid "NOTE: this setting cannot be changed later."
msgstr "SYLWER: ni ellir newid y gosodiad yma wedyn."

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:79
msgid "Number of spare devices for the RAID5 array:"
msgstr "Nifer o ddyfeisiau sbâr ar gyfer yr araë RAID5:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:84
msgid "Spare devices for the RAID5 multidisk device:"
msgstr "Dyfeisiau sbâr ar gyfer y dyfais amlddisg RAID5:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:84
msgid "You have chosen to create an RAID5 array with ${COUNT} spare devices."
msgstr "Rydych wedi dewis creu araë RAID5 gyda ${COUNT} dyfais sbâr."

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:84
msgid ""
"Please choose which partitions will be used as spare devices. You may choose "
"up to ${COUNT} partitions. If you choose less than ${COUNT} devices, the "
"remaining partitions will be added to the array as \"missing\". You will be "
"able to add them later to the array."
msgstr ""
"Os gwelwch yn dda, dewiswch pa rhaniadau a gaiff eu defnyddio fel dyfeisiau "
"sbâr. Cewch ddewis hyd at ${COUNT} rhaniad. Os ydych chi'n dewis llai na "
"${COUNT} dyfais, caiff y rhaniadau dros ben eu ychwanegu fel \"ar goll\". "
"Cewch eu hychwanegu nhw i'r araë yn hwyrach."

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:95
msgid "Active devices for the RAID0 multidisk device:"
msgstr "Dyfeisiau gweithredol ar gyfer y dyfais amlddisg RAID0:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:95
msgid ""
"You have chosen to create a RAID0 array. Please choose the active devices in "
"this array."
msgstr ""
"Rydych wedi dewis creu araë RAID0. Dewiswch y dyfeisiau gweithredol yn yr "
"araë hwn."

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:102
msgid "Active devices for the RAID1 multidisk device:"
msgstr "Dyfeisiau gweithredol ar gyfer y dyfais amlddisg RAID1:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:102
msgid "You have chosen to create an RAID1 array with ${COUNT} active devices."
msgstr "Rydych wedi dewis creu araë RAID1 gyda ${COUNT} dyfais gweithredol."

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:111
msgid "Active devices for the RAID5 multidisk device:"
msgstr "Dyfeisiau gweithredol ar gyfer y dyfais amlddisg RAID5:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:111
msgid "You have chosen to create an RAID5 array with ${COUNT} active devices."
msgstr "Rydych wedi dewis creu araë RAID5 gyda ${COUNT} dyfais gweithredol."

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:111
msgid ""
"Please choose which partitions are active devices. You must select exactly "
"${COUNT} partitions."
msgstr ""
"Os gwelwch yn dda, dewiswch pa rhaniadau sy'n ddyfeisiau gweithredol. Rhaid "
"i chi ddewis yn union ${COUNT} rhaniad."

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:119
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Diddymu"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:120
msgid "Multidisk device to be deleted:"
msgstr "Dyfais amlddisg i'w ddileu:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:120
msgid ""
"Deleting a multidisk device will stop it and clear the superblock of all its "
"components."
msgstr ""
"Bydd dileu dyfais amlddisg yn ei atal ac yn clirio'r uwchfloc o'i holl "
"gydrannau."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:120
msgid ""
"Please note this will not immediately allow you to reuse the partitions or "
"devices in a new multidisk device. The array will however be unusable after "
"the deletion."
msgstr ""
"Sylwer na fydd hyn yn caniatáu i chi ailddefnyddio'r rhaniadau na dyfeisiau "
"mewn dyfais amlddisg newydd yn syth. Fodd bynnag, ni ellir defnyddio'r araë "
"ar ol y dilëad."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:120
msgid ""
"If you select a device for deletion, you will get some information about it "
"and you will be given the option of aborting this operation."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych chi'n dewis dileu dyfais, cewch fanylion amdano a cyfle i beidio "
"mynd ymlaen â'r weithred."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:133
msgid "No multidisk devices available"
msgstr "Dim dyfeisiau amlddisg ar gael"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:133
msgid "No multidisk devices are available for deletion."
msgstr "Does dim dyfeisiau amlddisg ar gael i'w dileu."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:139
msgid "Really delete this multidisk device?"
msgstr "Gwir ddileu'r dyfais amlddisg hwn?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:139
msgid ""
"Please confirm whether you really want to delete the following multidisk "
"device:"
msgstr ""
"Os gwelwch yn dda, rhowch gadarnhad eich bod chi eisiau dileu'r dyfais "
"amlddisg canlynol:"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:139
msgid ""
" Device:            ${DEVICE}\n"
" Type:              ${TYPE}\n"
" Component devices:"
msgstr ""
" Dyfais:            ${DEVICE}\n"
" Math:              ${TYPE}\n"
" Dyfeisiau cydran:"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../mdcfg-utils.templates:139
msgid "${DEVICES}"
msgstr "${DEVICES}"
